data.description: Absolutely stunning 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home loaded with upgrades and luxurious features. This residence offers an array of modern amenities, making it a dream home for any family. Here are the key listing remarks to highlight the property:    This home boasts upgraded flooring throughout, featuring a harmonious blend of hardwood, tile, and vinyl plank. The rich, diverse textures add a touch of elegance to every room. You'll notice the meticulous attention to detail with crown molding and recessed lighting, complete with dimmers and decora switches that allow you to create the perfect ambiance. The kitchen is a culinary haven with 42" cabinets, granite countertops, a double oven gas range, under-cabinet lighting, and a stylish tile backsplash. The large island is a focal point of this stunning kitchen, allowing you to cook and entertain in style.    Upgraded bathrooms await upstairs. The primary bathroom provides a true spa-like retreat with a walk-in shower offering four shower functions (including a rain shower head and four body sprayers), a custom tile niche, and a bench. Enjoy the comfort and luxury of heated flooring with a thermostat to control the temperature. The quartz countertops offer timeless beauty in this luxurious bathroom. The bath fan even features Bluetooth capabilities. The hall bathroom boasts custom tile design with a niche, a jetted tub for relaxation, and a bath fan with Bluetooth connectivity. Truly, not a detail was missed with the bathrooms in this home!    The basement is an entertainer's paradise, featuring a kitchenette, raised seating for movie nights or game day gatherings, a large storage room with a laundry tub, and an additional room that could serve as a fifth bedroom. The basement bathroom has custom shower tile, niche, custom wall tile, and a unique feature - a urinal with a TV. Unprecedented luxury. As you step outside of the basement, you are greeted by a backyard that is a true oasis, with an in-ground saltwater pool (including a heater and electric cover) for endless summer enjoyment. There's also a paver grilling area, a cedar deck with waterproofing for the lower area, a stamped concrete patio, a paver fire-pit, cedar fencing for privacy, and even hot and cold-water hoses for convenience.    Don't miss this opportunity to own a home that blends modern convenience, luxury, and entertainment seamlessly. This property is perfect for creating cherished memories and enjoying every aspect of life to the fullest. *** Full list of property upgrades has been added to the documents section. ***
